{"tid":509642,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台中九日八夜自駕行程求批","createTime":"2017-12-25T14:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T05:04:47.000Z","uid":95663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3784859cab1ebe645300816e64c1b18944ef1ade","tid":509642,"uid":95663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"黎緊一月中會去台中玩幾日，資料搜集過好似啲地方都唔係咁順路..希望各巴絲可以俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay.1  台中機場》市區》中社花海》高美濕地》夜市》台中住<br />\n<br />\nDay.2 台中市區》攞車》彩虹眷村》妖怪村》忘憂森林》天梯風景區》嘉義或者關子嶺溫泉住<br />\n<br />\nDay.3 嘉義》阿里山》台中住<br />\n<br />\nDay.4 台中》清境》青青草原》清境住<br />\n<br />\nDay.5 武嶺睇日出、雲海》老英格蘭》小瑞士花園》台中<br />\n<br />\n淨底果幾日仲未plan好..諗過去唔去埋太魯閣公園"},{"pid":"688a81a70947b77c2f3f22e79a54dd38b9bfc712","tid":509642,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nDay.1  台中機場》市區》中社花海》高美濕地》夜市》台中住<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD.1 未有車？<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.imageupload.co.uk/images/2017/12/25/xxxa47a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imageupload.co.uk%2Fimages%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2Fxxxa47a9.png&h=b37349a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中社花海》高美濕地　相隔好遠喎<br />\n而后里同清水都同台中市距離相當遠<br />\n公車的士亦少<br />\n<br />\n你住咩位置？<br />\n要考慮喎。"},{"pid":"aef8e933172cd6573b18972955918e2a024252e5","tid":509642,"uid":95663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\nDay.1  台中機場》市區》中社花海》高美濕地》夜市》台中住<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD.1 未有車？<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.imageupload.co.uk/images/2017/12/25/xxxa47a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imageupload.co.uk%2Fimages%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2Fxxxa47a9.png&h=b37349a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中社花海》高美濕地　相隔好遠喎<br />\n而后里同清水都同台中市距離相當遠<br />\n公車的士亦少<br />\n<br />\n你住咩位置？<br />\n要考慮喎。</blockquote><br />\n終於有巴絲入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay1無租到呀，因為落機都差唔多晏就兩點..到時可能睇天氣再決定去高美抑或中社<br />\n<br />\n住就揀返逢甲附近，租車間公司都係果頭"},{"pid":"e71ad3e8f97da7ac064e6a8caefb1f99fa5c781a","tid":509642,"uid":864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"台中都玩九日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次四日已經覺得好夠"},{"pid":"37f8f512adbfc298e3d16363135f2e19413f36c7","tid":509642,"uid":10928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"去咁多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8852623b726b7cc48202d7dcdc75b4d4d19cec9","tid":509642,"uid":37165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:46:41.000Z","msg":"上次我去9日係落埋高雄<br />\n<br />\n你有車其實落埋彰化縣玩啦"},{"pid":"def282ad7c7965a4bd66b9574b657e1bb25938b4","tid":509642,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"即日來回阿里山好似太急<br />\n你有咁多日點解唔住一晚"},{"pid":"dafb6ad9a326fac73cfb72e37193192c74c1811f","tid":509642,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:46:45.000Z","msg":"日數就各有所好姐<br />\n未必一定要日日趕景點嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22ef9d38dbd3dece5b5a800a9febfe4a2f355dd","tid":509642,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aef8e933172cd6573b18972955918e2a024252e5","tid":509642,"uid":95663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\nDay.1  台中機場》市區》中社花海》高美濕地》夜市》台中住<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD.1 未有車？<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.imageupload.co.uk/images/2017/12/25/xxxa47a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imageupload.co.uk%2Fimages%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2Fxxxa47a9.png&h=b37349a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中社花海》高美濕地　相隔好遠喎<br />\n而后里同清水都同台中市距離相當遠<br />\n公車的士亦少<br />\n<br />\n你住咩位置？<br />\n要考慮喎。</blockquote><br />\n終於有巴絲入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay1無租到呀，因為落機都差唔多晏就兩點..到時可能睇天氣再決定去高美抑或中社<br />\n<br />\n住就揀返逢甲附近，租車間公司都係果頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:51:00.000Z","msg":"如果落機都差唔多晏就兩點<br />\n你不如直接出逢甲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為就算飛機航程唔遲<br />\n起飛亦未必準時<br />\n<br />\n即使咩都準時<br />\n又即使你無限金錢直接的士去<br />\n<br />\n果兩度(嘅其一)我唔認為你可以好輕鬆拖喼去<br />\n<br />\n勉強去只會為你做成負擔"},{"pid":"f6c78cfa2e6bc412b6561aeda8104907bac58310","tid":509642,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nDay.1  台中機場》市區》中社花海》高美濕地》夜市》台中住<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD.1 未有車？<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.imageupload.co.uk/images/2017/12/25/xxxa47a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imageupload.co.uk%2Fimages%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2Fxxxa47a9.png&h=b37349a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中社花海》高美濕地　相隔好遠喎<br />\n而后里同清水都同台中市距離相當遠<br />\n公車的士亦少<br />\n<br />\n你住咩位置？<br />\n要考慮喎。</blockquote><br />\n終於有巴絲入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay1無租到呀，因為落機都差唔多晏就兩點..到時可能睇天氣再決定去高美抑或中社<br />\n<br />\n住就揀返逢甲附近，租車間公司都係果頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>修正</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果落機都差唔多晏就兩點<br />\n你不如直接出逢甲<strong>(或者你嘅酒店先 唔知你住台中邊度 台中咁大)</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為就算飛機航程唔遲<br />\n起飛亦未必準時<br />\n<br />\n即使咩都準時<br />\n又即使你無限金錢直接的士去<br />\n<br />\n果兩度(嘅其一)我唔認為你可以好輕鬆拖喼去<br />\n<br />\n勉強去只會為你做成負擔"},{"pid":"f8c4718fdfe349ac26ad17d660b63d4d13f22228","tid":509642,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6c78cfa2e6bc412b6561aeda8104907bac58310","tid":509642,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T1